departments.name: Cardiology
departments.description: Heart and vascular system disorders, ECG and cardiac procedures.

departments.name: Neurology
departments.description: Brain, spinal cord and nervous system disorders.

departments.name: Orthopedics
departments.description: Bone, joint and muscle disorders including fractures and arthritis.

departments.name: Dermatology
departments.description: Skin, hair and nail conditions and treatments.

departments.name: Pediatrics
departments.description: Child health, growth, immunizations and neonatal care.

departments.name: Gynecology
departments.description: Women's reproductive health, pregnancy and related conditions.

departments.name: ENT
departments.description: Ear, Nose and Throat disorders and audiology.

departments.name: General Medicine
departments.description: Primary care, infections, chronic disease management.

departments.name: Urology
departments.description: Urinary tract and male reproductive system disorders.

departments.name: Ophthalmology
departments.description: Eye disorders, vision and ocular surgery.

diseases.name: Hypertension
diseases.diagnosis: Blood pressure monitoring, ECG, renal function tests.

diseases.name: Ischemic stroke
diseases.diagnosis: CT/MRI brain, CT angiography, carotid Doppler.

diseases.name: Migraine
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical history, neurological exam; MRI if atypical.

diseases.name: Eczema (Atopic dermatitis)
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, patch testing for allergens.

diseases.name: Acne vulgaris
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical evaluation, hormonal tests if severe.

diseases.name: Alopecia areata
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, scalp biopsy if needed.

diseases.name: Cellulitis
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, blood tests, culture if required.

diseases.name: Bronchitis (acute)
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, chest X-ray if needed.

diseases.name: Pneumonia
diseases.diagnosis: Chest X-ray, sputum culture, blood tests.

diseases.name: COVID-19
diseases.diagnosis: RT-PCR or antigen testing, chest imaging.

diseases.name: Sinusitis
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, CT sinus if chronic.

diseases.name: Uveitis
diseases.diagnosis: Slit lamp exam, referral for systemic workup.

diseases.name: Hyperparathyroidism
diseases.diagnosis: Serum calcium, PTH, bone density scan.

diseases.name: Irritable bowel syndrome
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical diagnosis, rule out organic causes.

diseases.name: Schizophrenia
diseases.diagnosis: Psychiatric evaluation, rule out medical causes.

diseases.name: Delirium
diseases.diagnosis: Clinical exam, review of medications and labs.

diseases.name: Pericarditis
symptoms: Chest pain relieved by sitting up
